0xDEA49773.name: GET_VEHICLE_HORN_TYPE

params.name: vehicle
params.description: The vehicle to check the horn type.

0xDEA49773.description:
This is a getter for the client-side native [`START_VEHICLE_HORN`](#\_0x9C8C6504B5B63D2C), which allows you to return the horn type of the vehicle.

**Note**: This native only gets the hash value set with `START_VEHICLE_HORN`. If a wrong hash is passed into `START_VEHICLE_HORN`, it will return this wrong hash.

```cpp
enum eHornTypes
{
    NORMAL = 1330140148,
    HELDDOWN = -2087385909,
    AGGRESSIVE = -92810745
}
```
0xDEA49773.resultsDescription: Returns the vehicle horn type hash, or `0` if one is not set.
